$\hat{\boldsymbol{\theta}}_1$ & $0.59$ & $0.55$ & $0.11$ & $0.62$ & $7.85$ & $-1.67$ & $-1.00$ & $0.00$ & $0.99$ & $1.43$ & $6.48$ & $1.00$ & $1.00$ \\
